Rough Magic is a 1995 comedy film directed by Clare Peploe and starring Bridget Fonda, Russell Crowe and Jim Broadbent. It was based on a novel by James Hadley Chase"Miss Shumway Waves A Wand", with the screenplay written by Robert Mundi, William Brookfield, and Clare Peploe.The film is set in the 1950s and focusses on a young magician who leaves her fianc√© to find a shaman in Mexico.
